9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to reckless driving; amending
Section 15, Chapter 366, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp.
11 2025, Section 20O), which relates to Class D2 felony
offenses; adding certain crime to list of D2 felony
12 offenses; amending 47 O.S. 2021, Section 11-901,
which relates to reckless driving; making certain
13 acts unlawful; providing penalties; and providing an
effective date.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 15, Chapter 366, O.S.L.
18 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 20O), is amended to read as
19 follows:
20 Section 20O. A. Upon the effective date of this act, Class D2
21 shall include the following criminal offenses:
22 1. Attempt to escape from penitentiary, as provided for in
23 Section 434 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma Statutes this title;
